          <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
          <description><![CDATA[HTML release notes]]></description>
          <enclosure
            url="https://lingcode.dev/LingCode-vX.Y-build<BUILD>-Installer.dmg"
            sparkle:edSignature="ed25519-signature-from-sign_update"
            length="bytes"
            type="application/octet-stream" />
        </item>

      ship.sh writes these items for you. Filenames now include the build
      number so each release gets a unique URL — no overwriting old DMGs,
      old signatures stay valid forever.
